Why Ameriprise Financial? | Ameriprise Financial



Skip to main content
























Why Ameriprise?
When you have the right financial advisor, life can be brilliant.
What matters most to you in life? It's a big question. But it's just one of the many questions an Ameriprise advisor will ask to get a better understanding of you, your goals and your dreams. Questions you might not hear from other advisors.
Together, you and your advisor will consider all aspects of your financial life ensuring as your life changes, your plan does too.
We'll help you plan to cover essential expenses and determine how to fund the lifestyle you seek, prepare for the unexpected and leave the legacy you desire. All to help you live confidently. Both today and well into the future.
Find an advisor who is right for you.
Start Here




How our Confident Retirement® approach is different
We'll help you feel confident about your financial future — at any stage in your life. You'll have straightforward conversations with your advisor, who will identify clear steps to help you reach your dreams and goals.
The plan you build together will address four key needs: covering essentials, ensuring lifestyle, preparing for the unexpected and leaving a legacy.


Essentials are the necessities — the monthly expenses that keep your life running
Lifestyle is about the things you want to do and how you want to live, today and in the future
The unexpected events that could derail your financial plans
Legacy is about the impact you’ll make on people and causes important to you


