A diverse set of solutions for a lifetime of needs
At Ameriprise Financial, you'll have access to a broad range of products and solutions offered by hundreds of providers — both nonproprietary and those under our Ameriprise, RiverSource and Columbia Threadneedle Investments brands. This wide variety means you have choices when it comes to determining the best course of action for each client.

 
At Ameriprise Financial, we believe all sound investment strategies first start with reputable investment research. The Ameriprise Investment Research Group (IRG) is dedicated to delivering independent and objective research based on their 300+ years of combined industry experience that includes eight Charter Financial Analysts, two Chartered Alternative Investment Analysts and one Certified Investment Management Analyst.
Once you have done your due diligence and are ready to recommend investments to your clients, you have access to a wide range of solutions based on the needs of your clients.
